local Players = game:GetService("Players") local RunService = game:GetService("RunService") local ReplicatedStorage = game:GetService("ReplicatedStorage") local TeleportService = game:GetService("TeleportService") local player = Players.LocalPlayer local playerGui = player:WaitForChild("PlayerGui") math.randomseed(tick())

local initialPos = Vector3.new(292.63, 4.00, -169.92) local repeatPos = Vector3.new(224.46, 4.19, -81.72) local interval = 3.5 local rejoinInterval = 225

local screenGui = Instance.new("ScreenGui") screenGui.Name = "InfoGUI" screenGui.ResetOnSpawn = false screenGui.Parent = playerGui

local frame = Instance.new("Frame") frame.Size = UDim2.new(0, 300, 0, 130) frame.Position = UDim2.new(0.5, -150, 0, 50) frame.BackgroundColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(20, 20, 20) frame.BorderColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(0, 170, 255) frame.BorderSizePixel = 2 frame.BackgroundTransparency = 0.05 frame.Parent = screenGui frame.Active = true frame.Draggable = true

local timeLabel = Instance.new("TextLabel") timeLabel.Size = UDim2.new(1, -20, 0, 50) timeLabel.Position = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0, 10) timeLabel.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 255, 255) timeLabel.BackgroundTransparency = 1 timeLabel.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold timeLabel.TextSize = 22 timeLabel.TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Center timeLabel.Parent = frame

local pointsLabel = Instance.new("TextLabel") pointsLabel.Size = UDim2.new(1, -20, 0, 40) pointsLabel.Position = UDim2.new(0, 10, 0, 70) pointsLabel.TextColor3 = Color3.fromRGB(255, 215, 0) pointsLabel.BackgroundTransparency = 1 pointsLabel.Font = Enum.Font.GothamBold pointsLabel.TextSize = 20 pointsLabel.TextXAlignment = Enum.TextXAlignment.Center pointsLabel.Parent = frame

local initialPoints = 0 local leaderstats = player:FindFirstChild("leaderstats") if leaderstats and leaderstats:FindFirstChild("Points") then initialPoints = leaderstats.Points.Value end

local startTime = tick()

local function moveTo(pos) local character = player.Character or player.CharacterAdded:Wait() local hrp = character:WaitForChild("HumanoidRootPart") hrp.CFrame = CFrame.new(pos) end

moveTo(initialPos)

local function fireStartMission() local startMissionRemote = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Events"):WaitForChild("StartMission") pcall(function() startMissionRemote:FireServer() end) end

local function fireMysteryCard() local remote = ReplicatedStorage:WaitForChild("Remotes"):WaitForChild("MysteryCardEvent") local cardNum = math.random(1, 3) local args = {[1] = "Card"..cardNum} pcall(function() remote:FireServer(unpack(args)) end) end

fireStartMission() fireMysteryCard()

RunService.RenderStepped:Connect(function() local elapsed = tick() - startTime local hours = math.floor(elapsed / 3600) local minutes = math.floor((elapsed % 3600) / 60) local seconds = math.floor(elapsed % 60) timeLabel.Text = string.format("الوقت: %02d:%02d:%02d", hours, minutes, seconds)

local currentPoints = 0
if leaderstats and leaderstats:FindFirstChild("Points") then
    currentPoints = leaderstats.Points.Value
end

pointsLabel.Text = "Points +: " .. (currentPoints - initialPoints)

end)

spawn(function() while true do wait(interval) local character = player.Character or player.CharacterAdded:Wait() local hrp = character:WaitForChild("HumanoidRootPart") local originalCFrame = hrp.CFrame

hrp.CFrame = CFrame.new(repeatPos)
    for i = 1, 2 do RunService.RenderStepped:Wait() end
    hrp.CFrame = originalCFrame
end

end)

spawn(function() while true do wait(rejoinInterval) TeleportService:Teleport(game.PlaceId, player) end end)

